---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import CallToAction from "@components/CallToAction.astro";
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  {/* Hero Section */}
  <header
    class="relative flex flex-col align-center justify-center py-32 text-white"
  >
    <img
      src="/muvco.webp"
      alt="The MUV Collective"
      class="absolute -z-20 min-h-full min-w-full object-cover filter brightness-50 saturate-0"
    />
    <h1
      class="text-center text-8xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6 drop-shadow-lg uppercase"
    >
      The MUV Collective
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-center text-2xl tracking-wide leading-snug max-w-[70ch] mx-auto mb-16 drop-shadow"
    >
      We help CrossFit and Fitness Athletes with their MUVment and mobility so
      they can stay in the gym and continue training without pain, stiffness, or
      limitations.
    </p>
    <div class="mx-auto">
      <CallToAction />
    </div>
  </header>

  {/* 3-Step Process Section */}
  <section class="mx-32 mt-32">
    <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Our 3-Step Process</h2>
    <ol class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 justify-center text-zinc-100">
      <li
        class="border border-zinc-800/10 bg-zinc-800 shadow-md rounded-lg px-8 py-10"
      >
        <span class="text-sm uppercase text-teal-400">Step 1</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-6">Assess & Test</h3>
        Get to the root of the problem and relieve pain and stiffness.
      </li>
      <li
        class="border border-zinc-800/10 bg-zinc-800 shadow-md rounded-lg px-8 py-10"
      >
        <span class="text-sm uppercase text-teal-400">Step 2</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-6">Fix Your MUVment</h3>
        Solve the root cause of the problem and improve your movement patterns.
      </li>
      <li
        class="border border-zinc-800/10 bg-zinc-800 shadow-md rounded-lg px-8 py-10"
      >
        <span class="text-sm uppercase text-teal-400">Step 3</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-6">Build Strength & Stability</h3>
        Teach you how to keep the problem from coming back and keep progressing.
      </li>
    </ol>
    <section class="my-12 flex justify-center align-center gap-8">
      <a
        href="/services"
        class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 hover:text-teal-400 focus:text-teal-400 hover:border-teal-400 focus:border-teal-400 px-8 py-3 text-xl duration-150 w-fit"
        target="
        _blank"
      >
        Read more about our services
      </a>
      <CallToAction />
    </section>
  </section>

  {/* About Section */}
  <section class="mx-32 mt-32">
    <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12">About Us</h2>
    <div class="flex gap-8">
      <Image src="/kyle2.webp" alt="Kyle Womack" height={600} width={600} />
      <div>
        <p class="leading-loose mb-12">
          MUV was founded by Dr. Kyle Womack to bridge the gap between the
          healthcare system and the gym. We focus on helping CrossFit, fitness,
          weightlifting, runners, and surfers continue their training without
          pain or need for unnecessary medications or surgeries. We help to
          improve any movement related issue you may be having so you can get
          you back to your activities fast, and come back better than before! We
          work in a hybrid approach that allows us to be able to help our
          athletes both in-person, as well as remotely.
        </p>
        <p
          class="leading-loose mb-16 border-l-2 border-teal-500 p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500/10 to-10% to-zinc-100"
        >
          <span class="font-bold">
            "I want people to have freedom of movement to live a high
            performance, pain-free lifestyle."
          </span><br /><span class="italic"
            >Dr. Kyle Womack, PT, DPT, CF-L2</span
          >
        </p>
        <section class="my-12 flex align-center gap-8">
          <a
            href="/about"
            class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 hover:text-teal-400 focus:text-teal-400 hover:border-teal-400 focus:border-teal-400 px-8 py-3 text-xl duration-150 w-fit"
            target="
        _blank"
          >
            Read more about us
          </a>
          <CallToAction />
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Testimonial Section */}
  <section class="my-32 mx-32">
    <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Testimonials</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <section
        class="border border-zinc-800/10 shadow-xl rounded-lg px-8 py-10"
      >
        <span class="text-sm uppercase text-teal-400">Cristy C.</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-6">Dr. Kyle Transformed My Life!</h3>
        Dr. Kyle is as honest and real as it gets! I was having lower back pain,
        so went for a consult. Turns out, my issue was not what I expected, but was
        a weak core. Who knew?! After a few sessions of retraining how to engage
        my core, understanding key positioning for training, breathing techniques,
        etc..... my back, mobility and overall sleep has made wonderful transformations.
        These simple techniques that Dr. Kyle has shown are life altering. I highly
        recommend to anyone.
      </section>
      <section
        class="border border-zinc-800/10 shadow-xl rounded-lg px-8 py-10"
      >
        <span class="text-sm uppercase text-teal-400">Krystyn L.</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-6">Better Shoulders, Better Lifts</h3>
        I’ve been working with Dr. Kyle for almost a year now. He helped identify
        the root causes of a bunch of things I had going on and had been working
        with me to get them fixed. Since I started working with him, my lifts have
        gotten better (be honest, it’s something we all want) and my movement patterns
        have improved tremendously. I don’t have pain in my shoulders anymore and
        that’s something that has been plaguing me for years now. I definitely recommend
        seeing him!
      </section>
      <section
        class="border border-zinc-800/10 shadow-xl rounded-lg px-8 py-10"
      >
        <span class="text-sm uppercase text-teal-400">Anne C.</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-6">Honest and Effective Treatment</h3>
        Excellent physical therapist and trainer. Really takes the time to work with
        you, and spends the whole hour with you. Understands athletes, athletic injuries,
        --and most importantly, how to fix them -- really well. More effective than
        chiro treatments, which can go on seemingly forever sometimes.
      </section>
    </div>
    <section class="my-12 flex justify-center align-center gap-8">
      <a
        href="/testimonials"
        class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 hover:text-teal-400 focus:text-teal-400 hover:border-teal-400 focus:border-teal-400 px-8 py-3 text-xl duration-150 w-fit"
        target="
        _blank"
      >
        Read more testimonials
      </a>
      <CallToAction />
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>
